nlq — the nlqdb CLI

Distribution channels aren't live yet (Phase 2, pre-release). Build
from source — requires Go 1.22+:

  git clone https://github.com/nlqdb/nlqdb
  cd nlqdb/cli && go build -o ~/.local/bin/nlq ./cmd/nlq

Release progress: https://github.com/nlqdb/nlqdb/issues?q=label%3Acli
